3d0669083cbad7a921b-768x355.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/dc081f56918398592a7e7641b13b8ecdaf9475028374b3d0669083cbad7a921b-1536x710.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/dc081f56918398592a7e7641b13b8ecdaf9475028374b3d0669083cbad7a921b.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">在 WWDC 中，Apple 展示了《Resident Evil 8: Village》在 Apple Ailicon 晶片，在 Mac 電腦運行。Capcom 高級技術研究部門經理 Masaru Ijuin 指，Macbook Air 可支援 1080P 運行《Resident Evil 8: Village》，而較高階的 Mac Studio 則可以以 4K 的畫質運行。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1103614" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/55a23dd0-e5da-11ec-ad7e-1811030d1e86-694x423.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="423" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/55a23dd0-e5da-11ec-ad7e-1811030d1e86-694x423.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/55a23dd0-e5da-11ec-ad7e-1811030d1e86-768x468.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/55a23dd0-e5da-11ec-ad7e-1811030d1e86.jpeg 1092w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">新版的《Resident Evil 8: Village》 會使用 Apple 開發的 MetalFX Upscaling 軟件運行，因此遊戲可在不需要強大 GPU 的情況下，創造色彩更豐富、更真實及流暢的畫面。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://www.digitaltrends.com/gaming/resident-evil-village-macos/">Digital Trends</a></span></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;theme=light&amp;color=white&amp;controls=0&amp;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><div class="feedflare">
