dth="400" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-07-12.53.20-400x580.png 400w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-07-12.53.20-620x900.png 620w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-07-12.53.20-768x1115.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-07-12.53.20.png 824w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 400px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">（圖片來源：<span class="s2"><a href="https://www.zdnet.com/finance/banking/wwdc-2022-buy-now-pay-later-with-apples-new-wallet-feature/">zdnet</a></span>）</p><p>除先買後付的服務外，Apple Pay 也支援智能訂單跟蹤購物，讓 Apple Wallet 中輕鬆看到其訂單何時到達。另外，Apple 亦宣佈由 7 月開始將在美國境內開放 iPhone 作為收款工具，只要是透過 Apple Pay 或信用卡支付，都能透過 iPhone 進行收款。</p><p class="p1"><span class="s1">資料</span><span class="s2">來源：<a href="https://www.zdnet.com/finance/banking/wwdc-2022-buy-now-pay-later-with-apples-new-wallet-feature/">zdnet</a></span></p><p class="p2">—</p><p class="p2"><span class="s3">unwire.hk</span> Mewe <span class="s4">專頁：</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span class="s3">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;theme=light&amp;color=white&amp;controls=0&amp;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><div class="feedflare">
